This license applies to WgSharp's own source code only. WgSharp optionally
downloads and uses the official, signed wintun.dll (Wintun) and wireguard.dll
(WireGuardNT) drivers at runtime; those drivers are separate components
authored by Jason A. Donenfeld / WireGuard LLC. Their underlying driver source
code is licensed under the GNU GPLv2, and is available in the author's own
repositories (git.zx2c4.com/wintun and git.zx2c4.com/wireguard-nt). The
prebuilt, signed DLL binaries that WgSharp actually downloads and uses are
distributed under WireGuard LLC's own "Prebuilt Binaries License" (included
in each driver's own download), which permits shipping the unmodified DLL
alongside other software via its documented API. Neither driver's source nor
binary is redistributed as part of this repository.
